Subject: Documentation-only recreation of the host cpio fix used during the RT2600ac build

The original standalone patch file used during the live Debian 13 build session was not preserved
in the OpenWrt tree. This file records that a host-side cpio configure/build compatibility fix was
required alongside the ninja Python 3.13 patch during the first successful build bring-up.

Treat this as an audit note, not as an authoritative upstream patch.

